data.description: Stunning, very gently lived in single story home in the heart of West Sherman, this was the model Wyldewood home for the community. Interior features clean lines, a modern color palette, & a huge kitchen with plenty of counter & storage space. The primary BDRM offers a private oasis with a walk-in closet & en-suite bath featuring a garden tub & separate shower along with dual vanities. The main closet connects to the laundry room for easy access. With 3 bdrms & 2 baths, this home boasts an open-concept design that maximizes space & natural light - the perfect combination of modern design & comfort. Enjoy the Texas weather on the covered patio & generously-sized backyard, perfect for entertaining. Conveniently located less than 10 minutes away from major commuting routes, shopping, Herman Baker Park and Sherman's booming tech center. Move in ready!! Schedule a viewing today and make it your own!
